            <p class="-mt-2 text-lg">Lunes a Viernes de 8 a 15 hs.</p>
          </div>

          <div class="relative pl-4">
            <div class="absolute left-0 top-0 bottom-0 w-0.5 bg-white/30"></div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold TxtBase2">Palermo</h3>
            <p class="mt-2 text-lg">Beruti 3345 PB</p>
